# Campus Life Planner

## Overview

Campus Life Planner is a vanilla JavaScript web application designed to help users manage campus events and activities. It allows users to create, edit, delete, search, and organize event records while practicing advanced JavaScript concepts such as regex validation, DOM manipulation, localStorage persistence, and dynamic UI updates.

The application follows a modular structure using separate JavaScript files for validation, UI rendering, search functionality, and data storage.

