---

## How to Run the Project

1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open index.html in a browser
3. Start adding events
4. Data will automatically save in the browser

---

## GitHub Pages Deployment

### Steps:

1. Push project to GitHub repository
2. Go to repository settings
3. Open "Pages" section
4. Under Source select:
   - Branch: main
   - Folder: root
5. Save and wait a few minutes

Your site will be available at:

https://Nzizadenilson.github.io/campus-life-planner/

---

## Notes

- This project uses only vanilla JavaScript (no frameworks)
- Fully client-side application
- Designed for learning regex, DOM manipulation, and state management
- All data is stored locally in the browser